252
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,680
<font color=#00FFFF>Was brauchst du noch?</font>

253
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:47,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Ein bisschen Salz, bisschen Pfeffer.</font>

254
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:49,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Und Majoran.</font>

255
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:52,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Jetzt haben wir</font>
