322
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:53,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Guck mal.</font>

323
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:55,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Bitte sehr.</font>

324
00:17:57,760 --> 00:18:00,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Ist es arg heiß?</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>- Nee, geht schon.</font>

325
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:02,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Mh.</font>
